@0 = ~There's nothing to do in this camp but drink and wait for our orders to head up to the front.~
@1 = ~Heard the news? Fort Ilkard isn't under siege anymore! They were just about to send me up to join the fighting, too. I think I'll have a drink to celebrate my good fortune!~
@2 = ~Word around the camp is that Fort Ilkard is under siege by one of them renegade barbarian tribes. I reckon they'll send some of us up there to join the fighting soon enough.~
@3 = ~Hey, you're <CHARNAME> - the hero of Neverwinter! I'd buy you a drink if they weren't so expensive in this dive!~
